extendedInfo.description: Point, drag and drop to pay your billsWith the mobile bank, you can access your accounts wherever you are.Without using your code generator, you quickly get an overview of all your current accounts, you can transfer between your own accounts and pay your eFakturas.Using your code generator, you can pay any bill on the fly.You can find the pin code for your card in the mobile bank, as well as enable or disable regional blocks. For this, you will need your code generator.You can easily get in touch with us through the mobile bank, and you can also block your card should you need to.
